00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:33,625
I lost. No.

49
00:03:33,708 --> 00:03:35,541
That was quite the experience.

50
00:03:35,625 --> 00:03:36,791
The unique
and unexpected delight

51
00:03:36,875 --> 00:03:39,166
at the center of your dish
was skillfully done,

52
