the delicate sweetness

55
00:03:46,458 --> 00:03:48,250
you had going
for the white bean paste.

56
00:03:48,333 --> 00:03:49,916
I agree with you.

57
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,625
However, Anne, you cast your
vote for Miss Tadokoro.

58
00:03:52,708 --> 00:03:54,333
Yes, I felt
it was rightfully hers.

59
00:03:54,416 --> 00:03:57,125
I had to give her credit
for her craftsmanship

60
00:03:57,208 --> 00:03:58,291
and what she accomplished.

61
00:03:58,375 --> 00:03:59,958
Urara:
Uh, anyway.

62
00:04:00,041 --> 00:04:02,625
For this card, victory goes
to the side of the Ten,

63
00:04:02,708 --> 00:04:05,208
to the famous
number third seat,

64
00:04:05,291 --> 00:04:07,375
Momo Akanegakubo!

65
00:04:07,458 --> 00:04:12,291
[ Cheers and applause ]

66
00:04:12,375 --> 00:04:15,500
Megumi.

67
00:04:15,583 --> 00:04:20,125
I'm sorry,
Some, Takumi.

68
00:04:20,208 --> 00:04:23,041
I lost this one.

69
00:04:23,125 --> 00:04:25,666
Nah, it's no biggie.
Don't pay it any mind.

70
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,833
That julienned ginger
was a good idea.

71
00:04:27,916 --> 00:04:29,041
You should be
very proud of it.

72
00:04:29,125 --> 00:04:31,625
That's right! You got nothing
to apologize for!

73
00:04:31,708 --> 00:04:32,666
Thanks for all
your hard work, Megumi.

74
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:35,375
Both: That was
a ballin' battle, bro!

75
00:04:35,458 --> 00:04:38,208
[ Giggles ]
That means a lot, everyone.

76
00:04:38,291 --> 00:04:41,250
What's with you?
You're not saying anything.

77
00:04:41,333 --> 00:04:44,000
Personally, I'm not thrilled
we've lost four bouts.

78
00:04:44,083 --> 00:04:45,666
Megumi.
Huh?

79
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,458
You fought well.

80
00:04:47,541 --> 00:04:49,250
Thanks.
Although, I'm sorry.

81
00:04:49,333 --> 00:04:52,208
I need to apologize
to Coach Kojiro

82
00:04:52,291 --> 00:04:55,541
Still,
I feel like I gave it my all.

83
00:04:55,625 --> 00:04:58,375
It's kind of incredible
that all things considered,

84
00:04:58,458 --> 00:05:01,291
I just went up against
a third year on the Ten.

85
00:05:01,375 --> 00:05:05,208
And so, that's why...
Uh --

86
00:05:05,291 --> 00:05:05,750
Megumi, please.

87
